QuestData.Title: Gut Guttra
QuestData.Description: Snowpaw was able to help me to here so that I might strike against their leader, Guttra, but I have lost too much blood. My time is near.$b$bDo you have the strength to help me avenge my fallen brothers and sisters and kill Guttra Wolfchew?$b$bThe monster resides in the tallest tower of Grimfrost.
